    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to deliver instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. To address platform-specific longevity, the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC Motorsports coated bearings, and both throttle actuators have been refreshed. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the original aluminum multi-link suspension geometry that provides exceptional mechanical grip and steering feedback. While the car shows minor cosmetic evidence of spirited road use, the drivetrain is robust, and the subframe has been inspected and found free of stress fractures. Recent service includes a fresh fill of 10W-60 synthetic oil and a brake fluid flush.",
