      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Finished in a sophisticated metallic charcoal, the exterior maintains a deep gloss, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor road-pebble marks on the front fascia consistent with regular, careful use. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment featuring premium leather upholstery that remains supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium navigation system and dual-zone climate control, is in full working order. Under the hood, the car has been consistently maintained with a documented service history; the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently inspected and cleared for many more miles. This is a reliable, well-cared-for example that looks great and drives even better.",
